race.comment: NAVYONTHEHIGHWAY (5) loves it here around the Doomben track with four wins from just six starts and will have taken a lot from that first-up victory here. Gets the services of Thornton in the saddle and should be right there at the business end again. BAND OF BROTHERS (7) will strip fitter second-up from the break and gets the reliable Dunn/Mallyon combination. Hard to toss in this suitable race. HATCHET (6) saves his best form for this course and distance with six wins and three seconds from just 12 spins. Genuine top-three prospects. OUR MAGNUS (15) is a last-start winner who draws low and gets in on the minimum weight. In the mix. EPIC PROPORTIONS (13) rounds out the selections.
